Calculates paper statistics

Uses anonymous functions to calculate columns from `USA` sheet in WOODCARB spreadsheet.

calcUSApaper()

Value

A data frame with necessary intermediate calculations to calculate carbon from paper. Corresponds with necessary columns from the `USA` sheet in the WOODCARB spreadsheet (list them?)

Examples

calcUSApaper()
